- <link>존 클루트|존 클루트</link> "Science Fiction: The Illustrated Encyclopedia". London: Dorling Kindersley, 1995. ISBN 0-7513-0202-3.
- <link>존 클루트|존 클루트</link>와 <link>피터 니콜스|피터 니콜스 (작가)</link> 편저., "<link>과학소설 백과사전|과학소설 백과사전</link>". St Albans, Herts, UK: Granada Publishing, 1979. ISBN 0-586-05380-8.
- <link>존 클루트|존 클루트</link>와 <link>피터 니콜스|피터 니콜스 (작가)</link>편저., "<link>과학소설 백과사전|과학소설 백과사전</link>". New York: St Martin's Press, 1995. ISBN 0-312-13486-X.
- <link>토마스 M. 디시|토마스 M. 디시</link> "The Dreams Our Stuff Is Made Of". New York: The Free Press, 1998. ISBN 978-0-684-82405-5.
- <link>프레드릭 제임슨|프레드릭 제임슨</link>. "미래의 고고학 Archaeologies of the Future: This Desire Called Utopia and Other Science Fictions." London and New York: Verso, 2005.
- <link>앤드류 밀너|앤드류 밀너</link>. "Locating Science Fiction". Liverpool: Liverpool University Press, 2012.
- <link>마수드 아르샤프 라자|마수드 아르샤프 라자</link>, Jason W. Ellis and Swaralipi Nandi. eds., "The Postnational Fantasy: Essays on Postcolonialism, Cosmopolitics and Science Fiction". McFarland 2011. ISBN 978-0-7864-6141-7.
- 로버트 레기날드. "Science Fiction and Fantasy Literature, 1975–1991". Detroit, MI/Washington, D.C./London: Gale Research, 1992. ISBN 0-8103-1825-3.
- <link>다코 수빈|다코 수빈</link>. "Metamorphoses of Science Fiction: on the Poetics and History of a Literary Genre." New Haven : Yale University Press, 1979.
- 유타 웰디스 편저. "To Seek Out New Worlds: Exploring Links between Science Fiction and World Politics". New York: Palgrave Macmillan, 2003. ISBN 0-312-29557-X.
- Westfahl, Gary, ed. "The Greenwood Encyclopedia of Science Fiction and Fantasy: Themes, Works, and Wonders" (three volumes). Westport, Conn.: Greenwood Press, 2005.
